imdb.title: Kiddy Girl-and
imdb.plot: Ascoeur and Q-feuille work as waitresses while they train to become members of the galaxy's shadow law enforcement agency, the ES Force.

episodes.title: Rakkî aitemu
episodes.plot: Ascoeur's bloomers cause a bit of an uproar in the café, but things take a turn for the worse when assassins show up for Chief Hiver. Can Ascouer save the day?

episodes.title: Amai, wana
episodes.plot: Ascoeur and Q-feuille go to great lengths to acquire more pudding for Ascoeur.

episodes.title: Saiaku no aishô?
episodes.plot: Ascoeur develops an infatuation with Troisienne that begins to irk Q-feuille.

episodes.title: Komori tokumu
episodes.plot: Chief Hiver finally assigns the girls a special mission - babysitting! While babysitting Di-air, Ascoeur and Q-feuille are attacked!

episodes.title: GOTT no bôrei
episodes.plot: While searching the abandoned GOTT building, Q-feuille gets separated from Ascoeur and Di-air and eventually stumbles across a shape-shifting monster!

episodes.title: Kyokuchô-shitsu no giwaku/Say You!
episodes.plot: Chief Hiver and Sommer are acting suspiciously, so the girls decide to spy on the pair. Later, Alisa takes the girls to a butler café.

episodes.title: Akogare no futari
episodes.plot: The girls accompany Trixie and Troisienne on a special mission, but they all run into trouble when they encounter two G Society members!

episodes.title: G Sosaeti
episodes.plot: While GTO prepares for their 25th anniversary celebration, the G Society makes some plans of their own.

episodes.title: Kinen shikiten
episodes.plot: GTO's anniversary celebration is interrupted by an attack from members of G Society.

episodes.title: Ikiteita, futari
episodes.plot: After the deadly anniversary assault, Ascoeur and Q-feuille are detrmined to become official ES members.

episodes.title: Shadou wâkâ
episodes.plot: Letuchaia uses her maid to spy on fellow G Society members to learn everything she can. Meanwhile back at GTO, the girls learn of G Society's plans.

episodes.title: Jikan no koori tsuita kûkan
episodes.plot: After learning of the Time Freeze Incident, the girls set out on a special mission.

episodes.title: Bakansu bakansu
episodes.plot: The girls are assigned a rescue mission on a female-only resort planet. The current visitors are trapped due to a malfunctioning security system.

episodes.title: Warui yume
episodes.plot: Ascoeur begins experiencing vivid dreams, and unknown to her, it is being caused by Shade. Later, she has an encounter with an unwelcome visitor.

episodes.title: Shiranai namae
episodes.plot: After being captured by G Society, Q-feuille loses almost all of her memories, but for some reason the name 'Ascouer' stays with her.

episodes.title: Hontô no watashi
episodes.plot: Di-air and Ascoeur head to the G Society headquarters to rescue Q-feuille, but when they arrive, Ascoeur begins experiencing flashbacks.

episodes.title: Yomigaeru kioku
episodes.plot: After a kiss from Geacht'er, Ascoeur's memories come flooding back to her.

episodes.title: Yomigaeru kNagare hajimeru jikanioku
episodes.plot: Geacht'er sets his plan into motion, and Ascoeur is unsure of what she should do next.

episodes.title: Tomaranai omoi
episodes.plot: Determined to destroy the Galaxy, Geacht'er does everything in his power to start time, but the GTO fleet has other plans.
